'''火星軌道探測器'''（{{lang-en|'''Mars Orbiter Mission'''}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]：'''MOM'''），或者非正式地稱為'''曼加里安號'''（Mangalyaan，{{lang-sa|मङ्गलयान}}，意為「火星飛船」），是[[印度太空研究組織|印度太空研究組織]]的火星環繞探測器，於2013年11月5日成功發射<ref name='Pro'>{{cite news |last=Walton |first=Zach |title=India Announces Mars Mission One Week After Curiosity Landing |url=http://www.webpronews.com/india-announces-mars-mission-one-week-after-curiosity-landing-2012-08 |date=15 August 2012 |work=Web Pro News |accessdate=8 September 2013 |archive-date=2017-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614071520/http://www.webpronews.com/india-announces-mars-mission-one-week-after-curiosity-landing-2012-08/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="India-20120815">{{cite news |authors=Staff |title=Manmohan Singh formally announces India's Mars mission |url=http://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/science/article3775271.ece |date=15 August 2012 |newspaper=[[印度教徒報|The Hindu]] |accessdate=31 August 2012 |archive-date=2016-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121185517/http://www.thehindu.com/sci-tech/science/article3775271.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYT-20120830">{{cite news |last=Bal |first=Hartosh Singh |title=BRICS in Space |url=http://latitude.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/08/30/india-and-china-race-to-send-a-mission-to-mars/ |date=30 August 2012 |newspaper=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=31 August 2012 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612162711/https://latitude.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/08/30/india-and-china-race-to-send-a-mission-to-mars/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。該次任務是一項「[[技術示範|技術示範]]」項目，目標是發展行星際探測任務必須的設計、規劃、管理和操作相關技術<ref name="ISSDC-201209">{{cite web |author=Staff |title=Mangalyaan -Mission Objectives |url=http://www.isro.org/pslv-c25/mission-objective.aspx |date=September 2012 |work=Indian Space Science Data Centre |accessdate=8 October 2013 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017141751/http://www.isro.org/pslv-c25/mission-objective.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
火星軌道探測器已於[[印度標準時間|印度標準時間]]2013年11月5日2:38 PM（9:08 UTC）在位於[[斯里赫里戈达岛|斯里赫里戈达岛]]的[[萨迪什·达万航天中心|萨迪什·达万航天中心]][[薩迪什·達萬太空中心第一發射台|第一發射台]]以 [[極軌衛星運載火箭|PSLV-XL C25]] 型火箭發射<ref>{{cite web|title=India’s Mars Mission Mangalyaan to be launched on November 5|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2013/10/indias-mars-mission-mangalyaan-to-be-launched-on-november-5/|accessdate=22 October 2013|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822031215/https://news.biharprabha.com/2013/10/indias-mars-mission-mangalyaan-to-be-launched-on-november-5/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該任務的發射窗口是在同年10月28日後約20日的時間內<ref name=launch/>。火星軌道探測器正式發射倒數計時開始於2013年11月3日06:08 AM，發射成功後結束。本項任務是印度的首個行星際探測任務。印度[[印度空间研究组织|ISRO]]是繼俄罗斯[[俄罗斯联邦航天局|RSA]]、美国[[NASA|NASA]]、欧洲[[ESA|ESA]]之後第四個成功進行火星任務的太空機構<ref name=DCCR>{{cite news|title=India to launch Mars Orbiter Mission: PM|url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/channels/sci-tech/space/india-launch-mars-orbiter-mission-pm-414|accessdate=13 October 2012|newspaper=deccanchronicle.com|archive-date=2012-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121121012120/http://www.deccanchronicle.com/channels/sci-tech/space/india-launch-mars-orbiter-mission-pm-414|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年11月30日 19:19 UTC，火星軌道探測器引擎开动23分钟进入[[霍曼轉移軌道|霍曼轉移軌道]]，离开地球轨道而进入飞向火星的[[日心軌道|日心軌道]]。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.isro.org/mars/updates.aspx | title = MOM- Latest Updates | accessdate = 30 November 2013 | date = 30 November 2013 | work = ISRO | archive-date = 2013-12-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203010404/http://isro.org/mars/updates.aspx | dead-url = no }}</ref>探測器旅行{{convert|780000000|km|mi}}的距离到达火星。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://spaceflightnow.com/pslv/c25/131105launch/#.Un4FzOIiEoM | title=Indian spacecraft soars on historic journey to Mars | accessdate=2014-09-25 | archive-date=2014-10-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008222818/http://spaceflightnow.com/pslv/c25/131105launch/#.Un4FzOIiEoM | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年9月24日，火星軌道探測器成功进入火星轨道。<ref>{{cite web|title=印度首个火星探测器进入火星轨道|url=http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140924/42069459_0.shtml|accessdate=2014年9月24日|archive-date=2014年9月24日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140924165617/http://news.ifeng.com/a/20140924/42069459_0.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 製作 ==
大部分技術和部件也是印度本土研發，耗資大約45億盧比（折合約七千四百萬美元），經費僅是美國太空總署的十分之一，是至今最省錢的火星探測項目，莫迪說比拍一部荷里活電影更便宜<ref>{{cite news|title=印度探測器 成功入火星軌道|url=http://paper.wenweipo.com/2014/09/25/GJ1409250018.htm|accessdate=2014年9月26日|newspaper=文匯報|date=2014年9月24日|archive-date=2014年9月27日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140927002816/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2014/09/25/GJ1409250018.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 任务载荷 ==
曼加里安號攜帶四台科研設備和一架照相機，預料環繞火星軌道至少六個月，分析火星大氣和地質，其中一個目標是嘗試尋找甲烷，以證明火星曾有生物存在。

项目总投资7300万美元，15千克（33磅）有效载荷包括五个科学仪器：<ref name="payload"/><ref name="Kumar">{{cite news | first = Kumar | last = Chellappan | title = Amangal to budget from Mangalyaan, say experts | date = 11 January 2013 | url = http://www.dailypioneer.com/home/online-channel/360-todays-newspaper/121404-amangal-to-budget-from-mangalyaan-say-experts.html | work = Daily Pioneer | accessdate = 11 January 2013 | archive-date = 2013-01-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130117051430/http://www.dailypioneer.com/home/online-channel/360-todays-newspaper/121404-amangal-to-budget-from-mangalyaan-say-experts.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Mars mission gets October, 2013 launch date deadline as India reaches out to the stars | date = 4 January 2013 | url = http://www.indianexpress.com/news/mars-mission-gets-october-2013-launch-date-deadline-as-india-reaches-out-to-the-stars/1054576/0 | work = The Indian Express | accessdate = 5 January 2013 | archive-date = 2013-01-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130108090211/http://www.indianexpress.com/news/mars-mission-gets-october-2013-launch-date-deadline-as-india-reaches-out-to-the-stars/1054576/0 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

